@startuml 11-double-write
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title Online Migration - Double Write Pattern

participant "Application" as app
participant "Old DB" as old_db
participant "New DB" as new_db
participant "Sync Job" as sync

== Phase 1: Enable Double Write ==

app -> old_db : Write
app -> new_db : Write (same data)

== Phase 2: Backfill Historical ==

sync -> old_db : Read historical
sync -> new_db : Write historical
note right: Skip conflicts\n(double-write wins)

== Phase 3: Verify ==

sync -> old_db : Checksum
sync -> new_db : Checksum
sync -> sync : Compare

== Phase 4: Switch Reads ==

app -> new_db : Read (10%)
app -> old_db : Read (90%)

note right: Gradually increase\nnew_db percentage

== Phase 5: Cutover ==

app -> new_db : Write only
app -[#red]->x old_db : Stop writes

note bottom
  **Zero Downtime Migration:**
  - No service interruption
  - Rollback possible until Phase 5
  - Data verified before cutover
end note

@enduml
